## Success Metrics Framework

> Standard metric categories. Features cite these and supply targets.

### Adoption

| Metric | Description | Tracking |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| Signup rate | New registrations per period | Analytics |
| Activation rate | Users completing first key action | Cohort |
| Time to value | Signup to first success | Event timing |

### Engagement

| Metric | Description | Tracking |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| DAU/MAU | Daily/monthly active users | Sessions |
| Feature usage | Per-feature adoption | Events |

### Quality

| Metric | Description | Tracking |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| Error rate | Errors per user action | Monitoring |
| p95 latency | Response time | APM |

### Business

| Metric | Description | Tracking |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| Retention | Weekly/monthly retention | Cohort |
| NPS | Net promoter score | Survey |

